description.displayText: Hannah was a wonderful part-time nanny for my little girl from 2-3 years old. She is definitely gifted with babies and young children. Hannah also has incredible music skills and is very artistic. They were always singing or creating something when I would come home. She always picked up the toys before I came home and was miraculous at helping my child nap. She was a pleasure to employ!

description.displayText: Hannah is extremely reliable and devoted to her calling to work with children. I have seen her caring for children and she immediately calms them and makes them feel comfortable. She is always looking for new things-toys, activities, stuffed animals to put into her "Nanny Bag". She loves to teach reading and sign language and is definitely an asset in any situation.
